{
  "stem": "24171.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as I took a look, like in the side, all the neighbors across the street, and little children their hand, they were looking, like, somebody-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was horrible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But one of the neighbors, which lived kind of-- and she came too, that one which we gave a lot of-- then came another one, which she had too, my sisters, a lot of linen.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have some of the sewing stuff, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] you know [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You asked what we were doing, once back home, the sports, or what, in the village before the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the girls had their kind of-- and there was no chores to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did all kinds of work, the needlepoint, and all those things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the wintertime, we had fun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, there is-- we used to have the feathers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we used to get the-- every Saturday night, with another house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the boys came too, if you had a boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The boys didn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They just kept company.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The girls were separating the little thing from the feathers, for the pillows, and for things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were reading, you know, some things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, we didn't have movies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had to go to [INAUDIBLE] where you had to walk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was just Saturday night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And if it was Sabbath, you were not allowed to walk after, without the [INAUDIBLE], without an [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I stood there, and one came running from the other neighbor there and hugged me, and kept on saying, don't worry, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She gave me back a few pieces of stuff.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was the homecoming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was, already-- we came home, like, in the middle of August.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
